{"tid":1297704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警惕] 警犬呢兩日無數嘅PR同小動作係為日後濫權升級鋪路","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T21:20:37.000Z","uid":168267,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"999f769292c1d3a85d4c6b48e5e24f46177eba06","tid":1297704,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"開錯台，再開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚警犬失晒控咁亂咬人，記者都郁埋，喺鏡頭前面完全唔避忌<br />\n見到有人話佢哋放棄形象<br />\n話盧sir權力被架空<br />\n亦有人問，點解和理優最後都會拉人打人<br />\n<br />\n今日我哋就見到，依家人哋不單止唔驚，仲動作多多<br />\n不停<span style=\"color: red;\">先發制人去合理化琴晚嘅行動，方便日後繼續以過度武力打壓和平示威者</span><br />\n１。公共關係科總警司：議員用好多粗口挑釁警方<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297082</a><br />\n２。警犬發表聲明指出九點開始既MK係非法集結<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfLzzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfLzzT</a><br />\n３。記協聲明失實 警方表遺憾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfKreT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfKreT</a><br />\n４。警察隊員佐級協會去信梁君彥 指兩議員妨礙警察工作<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297250</a><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有的士司機從業員總會譴責琴晚嘅司機伯伯<br />\n同埋M記唔交CCTV<br />\n呢啲你話佢哋自己醒水奶共，警犬冇背後做嘢，我就打死都唔信喇<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢哋讀得書少，但唔可以鬆懈<br />\n冇腦嗰班，係好認同政府同警察永遠是對的<br />\n啱先我屋企睇有線，老母聽見泛民聯合聲明譴責琴晚警方暴力就冷笑咗聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完呢啲９ｕｐ嘢，我哋成日笑完就算<br />\n但真係有批人會放咗喺心入便，慢慢會覺得差佬做嘢就係咁樣，而且依家人哋理直氣壯<br />\n<br />\n其實有咁多片、咁多證據，我哋可以做到啲咩去反擊？"},{"pid":"6d3077406027cd525ec89f9ca553ab7651803a82","tid":1297704,"uid":168267,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"大家討論下<br />\n依家警犬擺明要聯合香港各界嚟打擊示威者<br />\n經過一晚，我哋以為警犬會失民心<br />\n結果多咗的士司機從業員總會同M記兩個盟友（aka香港人清算對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n明明證據喺晒我哋度，警犬都咁高調燒到去梁君彥嗰疊，有兩個可能<br />\n１。令民意偏向屌９泛民，抵銷晏晝泛民聯合聲明嘅效果<br />\n２。背後已經扯撚晒貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論咩理由，以後佢哋要對議員郁手，都可以更輕易，更唔會引起民怨<br />\n<br />\n多謝啱先幫推嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d8831545a26c5641ec55b01bfd8b1609fdcec4","tid":1297704,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"2d1ea8f7fa407a3dbc3a6e775d8bb4ab1cce2c8d","tid":1297704,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求解"},{"pid":"dbf69fac82f5fefe800c172bb738ce4580eb2384","tid":1297704,"uid":256218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16230bb315ce770cd4d9870eaec52c1e3d90b774","tid":1297704,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"640703d5c4bbfe56cef0d20420ef6b180ce21e04","tid":1297704,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求解"},{"pid":"fd8c85ffd6f41fb7b69397e6dd0f2d8be018f45e","tid":1297704,"uid":119318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d3077406027cd525ec89f9ca553ab7651803a82","tid":1297704,"uid":168267,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"大家討論下<br />\n依家警犬擺明要聯合香港各界嚟打擊示威者<br />\n經過一晚，我哋以為警犬會失民心<br />\n結果多咗的士司機從業員總會同M記兩個盟友（aka香港人清算對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n明明證據喺晒我哋度，警犬都咁高調燒到去梁君彥嗰疊，有兩個可能<br />\n１。令民意偏向屌９泛民，抵銷晏晝泛民聯合聲明嘅效果<br />\n２。背後已經扯撚晒貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論咩理由，以後佢哋要對議員郁手，都可以更輕易，更唔會引起民怨<br />\n<br />\n多謝啱先幫推嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不過之前聽電台有的士大哥都話其實的總其實係唔代表佢哋<br />\n就算係有的士嗰啲的士佬都唔係咁易入到的總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbac1410a20e0fd25ba6f722d4434cc300939671","tid":1297704,"uid":267395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"各位下次真係要睇路 軍政府已經正式成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6540a3293176677820d53414a6339c6e26b09a09","tid":1297704,"uid":149849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac3721814ac67fb3d9933478dad652d9c158b139","tid":1297704,"uid":125027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:35:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得要話比所有人知，無論咩立場都好，唔應該比警權不受控。<br />\n就算係林奠，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢今日撐你做特首，聽日可以撐葉劉</span>，你永遠唔會知你係未成世都控制到佢地。<br />\n今日你比支槍佢，佢聽日可以令黎指住你。<br />\n傻撚左既政客先會支持警察濫權架炸，身在其中又點會唔知權力既誘惑。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐警既你答我: 今日你地冇事係因為佢地企係你果邊，咁聽日如果佢地企去另一邊呢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7f21ece576977f30f1d959b723dc777ded9d069","tid":1297704,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cp9dij2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCp9dij2.gif&h=f19a0291&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c02e14069c9978e8b7ebf47e50bd5a2c87f640f","tid":1297704,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislik